{"tid":923812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想笑on9仔既入黎","createTime":"2018-12-01T14:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T14:47:12.000Z","uid":54359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba748194de74254e87720f442ad1505a6708728","tid":923812,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"我就係果個on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說之前係波台派左2位巴打各200<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FMGSqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FMGSqc.png&h=b9b2a085&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGAMi5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGAMi5d.png&h=519f78d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後其中1位巴打第2日聲稱返左支那，叫我幫手再入<br />\n我都無咩所謂，本住連登有愛既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pz41SqY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpz41SqY.png&h=43be8eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho0P1jj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho0P1jj.png&h=dde497dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FNiUEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FNiUEk.png&h=19b6d3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後果位巴打好自然地被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJtqzEL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJtqzEL.png&h=d7019e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係要追返條數，亦都無預呢位巴打入返俾我，不過你交待返聲其實就ok，係信用問題<br />\n<br />\n呢擅野唔會影響我日後派俾其他巴打<br />\n有殺狗會大注一樣會派俾大家共享<br />\n請波台各巴打自重，守信<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴打恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係果句，連登有愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e413e91be45733c66ebf63c8398a8d6ca13422b9","tid":923812,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"b5f5007d374ec1268a369f7583c480fa4a9c1a71","tid":923812,"uid":210662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"做職乞好過返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa3b25bcff7389052ddd5c5d826254ae871171","tid":923812,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"派錢呢個風氣都on9啦<br />\n好熟咩三唔識七無啦啦派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知由幾時興起呢啲on9野"}]}